Governor Atiku Bagudu of Kebbi has approved the immediate payment of 2019 Leave Grant to workers on grade levels, GL 01 to 06. This is contained in a statement signed by the Acting State’s Head of Civil Service, Hajiya Fatima Sani-Ango in Birnin Kebbi on Wednesday. “The local government staff on grade level one to grade level seven (GL 1-7) will be paid, while the same applies to workers under the Local Government  Education Authority (LGEA),” she said.